      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One PM at a mid-stage B2B SaaS told me they used this approach to validate a new integration feature. They ran a two-question survey to power users over a weekend, collected 340 responses, and had enough confidence to green-light development by Monday morning. The Research Hub inside Survicate automatically grouped open-ended responses into themes — *\"Slack integration\"*, *\"API flexibility\"*, *\"pricing concern\"* — so the PM didn't have to read every single answer.",
